column2: SELECT  s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.z as z  FROM WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecPhotoAll  WHERE  SpecPhotoAll.nChild = # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_g > # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_z > # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_r > #) AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecObjAll  WHERE  SpecObjAll.z < # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_g > # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_r > #) AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid WHERE (s.class = &&& or s.class = &&&) ORDER BY s.z DESC
